summary:
Ned [seeing mysterio on tv]: This dude looks nice.
Peter: You supposed to stay by my side.
Ned: I like spider-man, but his cool...
body:
Ned [seeing mysterio on tv]: This dude looks nice.
Peter: You supposed to stay by my side.
Ned: I like spider-man, but his cool bro. No ofense. 
MJ: I prefer spider-man. 
Peter: See Ned. Someone that understand me. Thanks MJ. 
MJ: Not a big deal, Parker. I just think his suit fits better. 
Peter [staring at her]: So you think the spider-man is hot?
MJ: That's not what I said...
Ned: That's what you mean
MJ [leaving the room]: Bye losers...
Peter [smirking to Ned]: That's definitelly what she said.
Ned: Yeah!

“Oh yes, Friend Holly, this is an especially interesting bit of news for Hassi.”
